<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Reinhard II. und Johann von Hanau</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Reichel Nürnberger und Hans Maurer, beide Diener der Stadt, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_133" id="66r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_133_r1l23"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Reinharte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Hanaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_133_r1l24">Edlen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / darümb <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_133_r1l25">cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Reichel </del> edell den Reichel <expan>Nüremberg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_133_r1l26">diener / vveẏſer dicʒ briefs / mit euch dauon cʒureden / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_133_r1l28"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> viti Anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_133" id="66r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Reinharte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Hanaw</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edlen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt,
                                                darümb <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell den Reichel
                                                  <expan>Nüremberg<ex>er</ex></expan> und Hansen
                                                  <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener, weyser dicz
                                                briefs, mit euch davon czu reden. Und
                                                  <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
